  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "98f315c1-fd38-49a0-aa5e-3787dc7a014c",
    "name": "Playymate — Advanced Search & Discovery",
    "description": "Postman collection for NLP-Powered Advanced Search & Discovery module with OpenRouter LLM integration.\n\nFeatures:\n- 🔍 NLP Search (global, posts, accounts) - Now with OpenRouter LLM + rule-based fallback\n- 📍 Geo Search (nearby, map discovery, clusters)\n- 🔎 Filters & Suggestions (trending, autocomplete, filter presets)\n- 🎯 Personalized Recommendations (hybrid, collaborative, content-based)\n- 📊 Analytics & Tracking (search events, clicks, quality metrics)\n- ⚡ Performance Monitoring (metrics, health, slow queries)\n\n## NLP Engine\nThe search system uses a hybrid approach:\n1. **OpenRouter LLM** (primary) - Uses qwen model for intelligent NLP parsing\n2. **Rule-Based NLP** (fallback) - Regex patterns when LLM fails\n\nResponse includes `nlp_source` field showing which engine was used.\n\n## Setup\n1. Set the `base_url` variable to your server, e.g. `http://localhost:5000`\n2. Set `access_token` by running the Login request first.\n3. Ensure `OPENROUTER_ENABLED=true` in your .env for LLM-powered search.\n4. All IDs are auto-captured via test scripts.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "50779183",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/50779183-98f315c1-fd38-49a0-aa5e-3787dc7a014c?source=collection_link"
  },
